  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research study is to test whether a Computerized Rotational Head Impulse
      Test-Vertical (crHIT-vertical) is able to reliably evaluate the vertical semicircular canals
      in patients with vestibular dysfunctions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
